# IMPORTANT VIVA POINTS
# ================================================================
#
# 1. What is Data Wrangling?
#    Cleaning and transforming raw data.
#
# 2. Why normalization?
#    To bring all features to same scale.
#
# 3. Output range of MinMaxScaler?
#    0 to 1
#
# 4. What is Label Encoding?
#    Converting categories into numbers.
#
# 5. Problem with Label Encoding?
#    Model may assume order.
#
# 6. What is One-Hot Encoding?
#    Converts categories into binary columns.
#
# 7. Why One-Hot Encoding?
#    Removes false ordering.
#
# 8. What is Dummy Variable Trap?
#    Multicollinearity due to redundant columns.
#
# 9. Why drop_first=True?
#    Avoid dummy variable trap.
#
# 10. Difference:
#
# Label Encoding:
# Setosa -> 0
# Versicolor -> 1
# Virginica -> 2
#
# One-Hot Encoding:
# Setosa -> 100
# Versicolor -> 010
